<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This chapter does not modify in any manner the Communications Act of 1934 (<ref href="/us/usc/t47/s151">47 U.S.C. 151</ref> et seq.).</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id80ecd9ec-3a70-11f1-b817-c08bf6d1fe2c">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/217">Pub. L. 107–217</ref>, <date date="2002-08-21">Aug. 21, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1288">116 Stat. 1288</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
